'''朱莉娅-科隆纳环氧化反应'''（{{lang|en|Juliá–Colonna epoxidation}}）是一个以聚[[亮氨酸|亮氨酸]]为催化剂的碳-碳双键不对称环氧化反应。该反应在1980年由塞巴斯蒂安·朱莉婭（Sebastian Juliá）报道，<ref name = "Julia1">{{cite journal | last=Juliá | first=Sebastián | last2=Masana | first2=Jaume | last3=Vega | first3=Juan Carlos | title=“Synthetic Enzymes”. Highly Stereoselective Epoxidation of Chalcone in a Triphasic Toluene-Water-Poly[(S)-alanine] System | journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition in English | publisher=Wiley-Blackwell | volume=19 | issue=11 | year=1980 | issn=0570-0833 | doi=10.1002/anie.198009291 | pages=929–931}}</ref>以及由朱莉婭和斯蒂法諾·科隆納（Stefano Colonna）同时做的进一步阐述。<ref name = "Julia2">{{cite journal | last1 = Juliá | first1 = Sebastián | last2 = Guixer | first2 = Joan | last3 = Masana | first3 = Jaume | last4 = Rocas | first4 = José | last5 = Colonna | first5 = Stefano | last6 = Annuziata | first6 = Rita | last7 = Molinari | first7 = Henriette | title = Synthetic enzymes. Part 2. Catalytic asymmetric epoxidation by means of polyamino-acids in a triphase system | journal = [[J._Chem._Soc.,_Perkin_Trans._1|J. Chem. Soc., Perkin Trans. 1]] | pages = 1317 | year = 1982 | doi = 10.1039/P19820001317}}</ref>

[[File:Julia-Colonna_Epoxidation1.png|thumb]]

原始的反应模式为三相反应，包含了水相、有机相和催化剂相。作为反应物的[[查耳酮|查耳酮]]衍生物溶于有机溶剂（例如[[甲苯|甲苯]]或[[四氯化碳|四氯化碳]]）中，成为有机相。碱性过氧化氢溶液为水相。反应则发生在既不溶于水相，也不溶于有机相的催化剂聚亮氨酸的表面。[[两相|两相]]甚至[[均相|均相]]的改进方法也已开发出来，改进后的反应活性和速率均有显著提高。<ref name= "Allen">{{cite journal | last1 = Allen | first1 = Joanne V. | last2 = Bergeron | first2 = Sophie | last3 = Griffiths | first3 = Matthew J. | last4 = Mukherjee | first4 = Shubhasish | last5 = Roberts | first5 = Stanley M. | last6 = Williamson | first6 = Natalie M. | last7 = Wu | first7 = L. Eduardo | title = Juliá–Colonna asymmetric epoxidation reactions under non-aqueous conditions: rapid, highly regio- and stereo-selective transformations using a cheap, recyclable catalyst | journal = [[J._Chem._Soc.,_Perkin_Trans._1|J. Chem. Soc., Perkin Trans. 1]] | pages = 3171 | year = 1998 | doi = 10.1039/A805407J | issue = 19}}</ref><ref name= "Flood">{{cite journal | last1 = Flood | first1 = Robert W. | last2 = Geller | first2 = Thomas P. | last3 = Petty | first3 = Sarah A. | last4 = Roberts | first4 = Stanley M. | last5 = Skidmore | first5 = John | last6 = Volk | first6 = Martin | title = Efficient Asymmetric Epoxidation of α,β-Unsaturated Ketones Using a Soluble Triblock Polyethylene Glycol−Polyamino Acid Catalyst | journal = [[Org._Lett.|Org. Lett.]] | volume = 3 | pages = 683 | year = 2001 | doi = 10.1021/ol007005l | issue = 5}}</ref>

该反应是在温和条件下，立体选择性地环氧化双键的有效手段，因而在有机合成上具有重大的价值:环氧化物不仅是许多有机合成的中间体，许多天然产物也都是过氧化物。此外，经 [http://www.bayer.com/ 拜耳] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bayer.com/ |date=20110220223026 }}（Bayer）和[http://corporate.evonik.com/en/Pages/default.aspx/ 埃佛歷克] {{Wayback|url=http://corporate.evonik.com/en/Pages/default.aspx/ |date=20200207054934 }}（Evonik）等人的工作，该反应已经能够有效地应用于工业生产。最后，该反应的催化剂聚氨基酸具有类似[[酶|酶]]的性质，因而该反应也有助于对[[生源合成|生源合成]]的研究。<ref name= "Carrea1">{{cite journal | last1 = Carrea | first1 = G | last2 = Colonna | first2 = S | last3 = Kelly | first3 = D | last4 = Lazcano | first4 = A | last5 = Ottolina | first5 = G | last6 = Roberts | first6 = S | title = Polyamino acids as synthetic enzymes: mechanism, applications and relevance to prebiotic catalysis | journal = [[Trends_in_Biotech|Trends in Biotech]] | volume = 23 | pages = 507 | year = 2005 | doi = 10.1016/j.tibtech.2005.07.010 | issue = 10}}</ref><ref name= "Kelly1">{{cite journal | last1 = Kelly | first1 = David R. | last2 = Meek | first2 = Alastair | last3 = Roberts | first3 = Stanley M. | title = Chiral amplification by polypeptides and its relevance to prebiotic catalysis | journal = [[Chem._Comm.|Chem. Comm.]] | pages = 2021 | year = 2004 | doi = 10.1039/B404379K | issue = 18}}</ref>

==反应机理==
朱莉娅-科隆纳氧化反应本质上是缺电子碳-碳双键（例如α,β不饱和酮中的碳-碳双键）的不对称亲核环氧化反应。图 2展示了亲核环氧化反应的一般机理，在此反应中，聚亮氨酸作为催化剂控制反应。

[[File:Julia-Colonna_Epoxidation_Mechanism3.png|center]]
过氧化氢阴离子与查耳酮在聚亮氨酸催化剂中形成复合物，然后反应生成过氧化物阴离子中间体。中间体在催化剂结构的控制下迅速关环，立体选择性地形成产物环氧化物。

